Speaker 1: I was just explaining to you, we don't do one-time orders.

Speaker 1: so it needs to have a set refill date.

Speaker 2: You can always modify it, though,

Speaker 1: but it does need to have that to ship out.

Speaker 1: Robinson, 401501.

Speaker 1: for a new Viagra AGV.

Speaker 1: I cancel these orders out, sir, you

Speaker 2: wouldn't be able to access this anymore,

Speaker 1: because the doctor would delete the prescription.

Speaker 2: However, I can always just freeze out your account

Speaker 1: to our every six-month freeze plan.

Speaker 2: That way, you could just call us when you require them

Speaker 1: or call us to delay them, and you'll still

Speaker 2: have access to it for when you need it.

Speaker 1: Now, let's just cancel it.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: Just keep in mind, sir, you wouldn't

Speaker 2: be able to access this moving forward,

Speaker 1: as the visit itself will be canceled out,

Speaker 2: and they're not going to cover another visit.

Speaker 1: OK, next time.

Speaker 2: No worries.

Speaker 1: You're all set, then.

Speaker 2: I cancel that out for you, and you're good to go.

Speaker 1: Hope you have a great day.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Bye.

Speaker 2: No worries.

Speaker 1: Goodbye.
